reviewText: I still look at this DVD as a review to gain more inspiration. This guy is a very awesome metal guitarist! And I play Punk Rock guitar, but I do get inspired by Metal music. This happens to be the best Rock House Method DVD out there, it has won several awards as Instructional Products of the Year for 2008, 2009, 2010
A lot of great examples, very happy with it so far
I am really of the opinion that even a little tip can make things worth it in guitar. Thus, I got tips here.  It isn't awesome but if you like COB or appreciate Alexi's talent, it's worth a checkout.
